\begin{mdInlineSnippet}[be3f06595012e1b8491f993a03d695fd]%mdk
$Naive~Approach$\end{mdInlineSnippet}%mdk
%mdk-data-line={323}
\begin{mdInlineSnippet}[b21f776fc1b2d5430fb9925d6a6f0c48]%mdk
$\begin{aligned}T(n) &= Translate(n) * Rotate(n) * AddDetect(n)\\Translate(n) &= \mathcal{O}(n^2)\\ Rotate(n) &= \Theta(1)\\AddDetect(n) &= \mathcal{O}(n^2)\\T(n) &= \mathcal{O}(n^2) * \Theta(1) * \mathcal{O}(n^2)\\&= \mathcal{O}(n^4)\end{aligned}$\end{mdInlineSnippet}%mdk
%mdk-data-line={334}
\begin{mdDisplaySnippet}[279951e3f3ecaa800dec1989564fb8e8]%mdk
\[%mdk-data-line={335}
  T(n) = \mathcal{O}(n^4)
\]%mdk
\end{mdDisplaySnippet}%mdk
%mdk-data-line={339}

$\begin{aligned}T(N) &= \Theta(N \log (N))\\N &= \mathcal{O}(n^2)\\ T(N) &= \mathcal{O}(n^2 \log(n^2))\\\log(n^2) &= 2 \log (n)\\T(N) &= \mathcal{O}(2 n^2 \log(n))\\&= \mathcal{O}(n^2 \log n)\\\end{aligned}$\end{mdInlineSnippet}%mdk
